AC Milan&rsquo;s midfielder, who is currently on loan at Spezia, Tommaso Pobega spoke to Radio Sportiva, and this is what he said:<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I hope I did Milanello a pleasure for the goal in the game against Napoli. I&rsquo;m focused on Spezia. I am friends with several people at Milan, I talk often with Gabbia, it would be nice to be comrades again in the future. However, I think that now I have to improve in order to always be ready to play for Milan too.&rdquo;

